generated/
test/fixtures/public/
test/fixtures/images/
test/fixtures/generated/
plugins/imagegen/test/fixtures/public/
plugins/imagegen/test/fixtures/images/
plugins/imagegen/test/fixtures/generated/

# Per-user Claude Code state (NEVER commit — contains personal enabled-plugins
